9 §1963. Unfair methods and unfair or deceptive acts and practices prohibited
10 No person shall engage in this state in any trade practice which is or act
11 affecting the business of insurance as defined in this Part to be an unfair method of
12 competition or an unfair or deceptive act or practice in the conduct of the business
13 of insurance, including unauthorized insurance as provided in R.S. 22:1902 et seq.
14 or the failure to maintain professional liability insurance, if such coverage is required
15 pursuant to R.S. 22:1570.1.
